module REQ_FLIGHT_DISPATCHER_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-FLIGHT-DISPATCHER-01
 * Title       : Register Flights with Estimated Times
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
